SIMPLE: seventeen
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Seventeen
<hw>Sev"en*teen`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>seventene</ets>, AS. <ets>seofont⟦ymac⟧ne</ets>, i. e.,
<ets>seven-ten</ets>. Cf. <er>Seventy</er>.]</ety> <def>One more than
sixteen; ten and seven added; <as>as, <ex>seventeen</ex>
years</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seventeen</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Seventeen
<hw>Sev"en*teen`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The number greater
by one than sixteen; the sum of ten and seven; seventeen units or
objects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A symbol denoting seventeen units, as 17, or
xvii.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seventeenth</ent>⟦br⟧
